description:
DISCIPLINE! The 14th Ultimate 30-Minute Motivational Speech Compilation is here! These are some of the BEST Motivational Speeches you'll ever hear, featuring powerful speeches on Discipline featuring Freddy Fri (https://bit.ly/FreddyFriMotiversity), Will Hollis (https://bit.ly/WilliamHollisMotiversity) and more!


Music by Really Slow Motion (https://bit.ly/RSMMusic), and Audiomachine (https://www.youtube.com/audiomachine).
